<plot>A Winter Tale tells the emotional story of a Black men's support group that begins to meet at the local Caribbean Takeaway restaurant following the shooting death of a young child. It features a talented ensemble cast led by Canadian stars Peter Williams and Michael Miller and Caribbean icons Leonie Forbes and Dennis "Spranglang" Hall. The script was developed through a collaborative improvisational process with the cast, and shot on location in Toronto's Parkdale community.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?018321</url></doc>
